      "id": "PopularPost263566",
      "post_content": "It was a neat combat trick in limited, at the time, I'm sure. As it stands, the lack of preventing damage to players (or planeswalkers) seal its fate. It's bad. See [Fog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog) and [Holy Day](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day) for examples of how to do this better, for cheaper. And see [Safe Passage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Safe Passage)'s rating for how valuable the added protection is considered to be. It costs more, and it's still better.",
